        <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);line-height:1.8;"><strong style="color:#f5d07a;">Navigating a post-report negotiation?</strong> The inspection condition period is one of the moments in a sale where experienced agent guidance matters most. Daniel has handled building and pest report negotiations across Brisbane's inner east and can help you calibrate your response to buyer requests without leaving money on the table or losing a genuine buyer over routine findings. <a href="/contact" style="color:#f5d07a;font-weight:600;">Get in touch.</a></p>
      </div>

